Detailed Description

BtDataElement is the base class for all kinds of data elements. A data element is a unit that has a size, a type and a value. The type determines how the value has to be interpreted. Some member functions are implemented as pure virtual functions, so this class is abstract and can never be instantiated. It only forms a basic interface to query some informations that are necessary for type casting.
